				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all

1576835924--
			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10

1576836110--
			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10

1576836765--
			select num_iid,sku_id,title,prd_no,pic_path,sku_properties_name as sku_name from (
				select num_iid,'' as sku_id,title,(case when replace_prd_no = '' then outer_iid else replace_prd_no end) AS prd_no,pic as pic_path,'' AS sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online
				where have_sku= '0' 
				union all
				select aa.num_iid,aa.sku_id,bb.title,(CASE WHEN aa.replace_prd_no != '' THEN aa.replace_prd_no WHEN bb.replace_prd_no != '' THEN bb.replace_prd_no  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id != '' THEN aa.outer_sku_id  WHEN aa.outer_sku_id = '' AND aa.outer_iid != ''  THEN aa.outer_iid ELSE aa.num_iid END) AS prd_no,
				aa.pic as pic_path,aa.sku_properties_name from u13123456789_product_online_sku aa
				inner join (select num_iid,title,replace_prd_no from u13123456789_product_online) bb ON aa.num_iid=bb.num_iid
				where 1=1 
				
			) a limit 0,10
